page.title: 01TYSOE 1985
page.content: Tysoe is a predominantly agricultural village situated in the rural area of Warwickshire. The information detailed has been chosen specifically to give an informative and revealing picture of this village in 1985 by recording topics such as farming, landscape, ecology which seem particularly relevant to this area; population, housing, trade and education, which provide details of residents, where they live, commercial enterprise, and their children's educational prospects home life, arts and crafts, clubs, which high-light family and domestic life, artistic aspects and leisure, religion, attitudes which highlight general beliefs and local history of the village.
